WEBVTT

01:05.010 --> 01:06.780
Around 01:20

01:06.780 --> 01:09.070
three members of North Korean Special Forces

01:09.070 --> 01:11.170
crossed the Military Demarcation Line.

01:11.170 --> 01:14.270
They invaded our Guard Post 301

01:14.270 --> 01:16.220
and took hostage two of our soldiers

01:16.220 --> 01:18.180
who were on guard duty.

01:18.180 --> 01:21.050
And they are currently in sit-in demonstration.

01:22.240 --> 01:23.430
Sit-in demonstration?

01:23.870 --> 01:25.980
Are they trying to start a war

01:25.980 --> 01:27.860
by sending over three soldiers?

01:29.210 --> 01:31.289
They are just trying to provoke us.

01:31.289 --> 01:32.870
In the DMZ,

01:32.870 --> 01:36.860
the one who fires first violates the Korean Armistice Agreement.

01:36.860 --> 01:38.320
In order to negotiate better deals

01:38.320 --> 01:40.259
in the upcoming six-party talks,

01:40.259 --> 01:41.810
they are trying to

01:41.810 --> 01:45.770
instigate us to use military force first.

01:49.580 --> 01:51.680
So what should we do?

01:51.680 --> 01:54.410
We can't attack them first.

01:54.410 --> 01:57.950
But our soldiers are being held hostages.

01:57.950 --> 02:00.100
We can't just sit around doing nothing.

02:00.430 --> 02:02.270
We have to send them back quietly.

02:03.420 --> 02:06.540
We dispatched Alpha Team of the Special Forces.

02:16.640 --> 02:17.940
Freeze! Who are you?

02:20.710 --> 02:22.390
I am Yoo Shi Jin, Captain of the Alpha Team.

02:22.710 --> 02:23.360
From now on,

02:23.360 --> 02:26.440
the Alpha Team is in charge of this operation.

02:45.079 --> 02:46.340
What are you doing?

02:46.340 --> 02:47.800
Since this is the DMZ,

02:48.200 --> 02:49.640
we need to talk it out.

03:05.970 --> 03:07.940
I'm the captain in command.

03:09.440 --> 03:11.570
Are our soldiers okay in there?

03:13.930 --> 03:16.540
Why don't we stop here? We'll send you home safely.

03:16.890 --> 03:18.760
It seems that they would not give up that easily.

03:19.660 --> 03:20.760
Let us go in.

03:24.450 --> 03:27.370
This is Big Boss. I'm going in with Wild Wolf.

03:29.680 --> 03:32.230
This is Piccolo. Location confirmed.

03:39.570 --> 03:41.730
This is Sooryu. The explosives are set up.

03:42.010 --> 03:43.600
Harry Potter is ready.

03:44.440 --> 03:45.579
Explosives?

03:45.760 --> 03:47.490
Then what about these two?

03:47.490 --> 03:50.250
It's the last resort in case the talk fails.

03:54.079 --> 03:55.590
We'll open a gate for your retreat.

03:55.590 --> 03:57.140
Stop it and go home.

03:58.660 --> 04:00.450
Things will only get complicated when dawn breaks.

04:01.380 --> 04:02.560
You better go when we let you.

04:41.050 --> 04:42.360
We can't just go empty-handed.

04:50.640 --> 04:54.159
Before we leave in name of a republic soldier,

04:54.159 --> 04:56.600
we need to kill some special force members of South Korean.

05:02.540 --> 05:03.660
Okay.

05:05.390 --> 05:06.580
Come on then.

06:19.210 --> 06:21.870
Were you always right-handed?

07:56.010 --> 08:00.080
You. You can't kill me.

08:00.640 --> 08:04.060
People of South Korea can only talk

08:04.380 --> 08:05.930
but never fire first.

08:07.340 --> 08:10.720
We republic country is different.

08:14.050 --> 08:15.750
After 70 years of separation

08:15.750 --> 08:17.300
you still have such a misunderstanding to us.

08:17.300 --> 08:21.130
If it's for the peace of our country,

08:21.130 --> 08:21.880
no matter where or when,

08:21.880 --> 08:23.280
we never miss a target.

08:31.050 --> 08:32.659
Don't make a mistake.

08:33.770 --> 08:34.860
I don't stop my enemy

08:34.860 --> 08:36.299
when he makes a mistake.

08:36.299 --> 08:38.370
I came here as a warrior.

08:38.370 --> 08:40.429
I can't go back dead.

08:42.789 --> 08:44.169
Put your guns down.

08:47.530 --> 08:50.600
I am glad to meet you, Captain Yoo Shi Jin.

08:50.600 --> 08:54.760
I understand, but don't make this an annual event.

08:55.590 --> 08:56.980
Senior Lieutenant An Jung Joon.

09:10.050 --> 09:10.870
Let's go.

09:17.400 --> 09:22.270
This is Big Boss. Alpha Team has completed the mission.

09:57.100 --> 09:58.930
Did you shoot with your eyes closed?

09:58.930 --> 10:00.650
You’re a second class soldier.

10:00.650 --> 10:03.420
Don't you think the barrel is a bit bent?

10:03.420 --> 10:05.800
I can’t adjust the trigger. It has a bad hit rate too.

10:06.640 --> 10:07.780
It’s crap.

10:08.290 --> 10:09.570
Will you play one more round?

10:09.570 --> 10:12.810
Well… Why can't this click correctly?

10:14.310 --> 10:16.650
You can't touch it like that.

10:16.650 --> 10:17.620
This is…

10:17.620 --> 10:20.500
a model based on the gun

10:20.500 --> 10:23.710
American Delta Forces used in the desert.

10:23.710 --> 10:25.600
So if you use it as your guns in the military,

10:26.530 --> 10:27.780
it will surely break.

10:28.690 --> 10:31.020
Thief! He's a thief!

10:31.880 --> 10:33.380
Hey! Catch that thief!

10:33.380 --> 10:35.990
He's a thief! Catch him!

10:35.990 --> 10:38.210
He’s running towards this way.

10:38.570 --> 10:39.920
Let me borrow this.

10:41.360 --> 10:44.110
Ow. But we are on vacation!

10:47.690 --> 10:48.280
Since it's a toy,

10:48.280 --> 10:50.750
it' got a shot range of about five meters.

10:50.750 --> 10:52.710
Now the target is ten meters from us.

10:56.010 --> 10:57.140
Seven meters.

10:58.640 --> 11:00.540
Hey, you…

11:00.540 --> 11:01.910
Five meters.

11:06.290 --> 11:07.610
Now.

11:36.540 --> 11:37.800
The scooter seems fine.

11:38.360 --> 11:39.560
Did you call the police?

11:39.560 --> 11:42.350
Don't worry about it. It'll be more trouble

11:42.350 --> 11:44.240
if they bug me about the coupon thief.

11:44.240 --> 11:47.490
Anyway, I have nothing to do with his injuries.

11:47.490 --> 11:49.500
So don't call me to the station, okay?

11:58.860 --> 11:59.640
Thank you.

11:59.990 --> 12:01.680
Hi. Someone got hurt in a motorcycle accident.

12:04.510 --> 12:06.020
Leave it. It doesn't hurt.

12:08.600 --> 12:09.780
Just lie down.

12:10.290 --> 12:11.520
If you move, you could ruin your spine.

12:11.520 --> 12:12.900
And you’ll be in suffering for your whole life.

12:16.180 --> 12:17.890
Whoa! What are you trying to do?

12:18.230 --> 12:19.680
To realize social justice,

12:19.680 --> 12:21.240
I’m giving first aid to the thief.

12:25.770 --> 12:28.190
Could you sell me your dolls?

12:29.820 --> 12:31.830
Those? They aren't for sale.

12:31.830 --> 12:33.270
You better sell them.

12:34.140 --> 12:37.010
Otherwise I will just win them all.

12:39.300 --> 12:42.630
Oh, if you have a pen, let me borrow it.

12:44.220 --> 12:45.390
A… A pen?

13:02.830 --> 13:04.330
Your girlfriend is really pretty.

13:04.540 --> 13:06.520
I feel like I've met the girl of my dreams.

13:07.290 --> 13:09.140
Your dolls look great together.

13:10.940 --> 13:12.720
This is my comrade.

13:13.370 --> 13:18.570
Geez! Why did you accept them?

13:18.570 --> 13:19.910
How could I say no

13:19.910 --> 13:20.680
when he offered them,

13:20.680 --> 13:21.910
begging us not to come back?

13:23.660 --> 13:24.640
I wonder how a softie like you

13:24.640 --> 13:26.350
how can you be a gang member.

13:27.370 --> 13:28.910
The longer we stay together, the less I know you.

13:30.520 --> 13:33.050
The guy earlier will be fine, right?

13:33.420 --> 13:35.490
He knew how to fall on his side when

13:35.490 --> 13:37.540
he was falling off the scooter.

13:38.140 --> 13:40.090
He's athletic. He'll be fine.

13:41.800 --> 13:43.880
I was in his age.

13:45.060 --> 13:47.520
An athlete should meet a good person to lead him.

13:47.940 --> 13:50.200
Why? Are you worried about him?

13:50.800 --> 13:52.570
Does he remind you of your dark days?

13:53.810 --> 13:55.900
I kind of feel sorry for him.

13:57.560 --> 14:00.820
Did you do a lot of bad things when you were his age?

14:00.820 --> 14:02.510
I was the commander.

14:03.280 --> 14:05.440
Gosh, so your story is a noir.

14:05.440 --> 14:07.390
But he's just a mere criminal.

14:07.660 --> 14:09.200
You are so cruel.

14:10.910 --> 14:13.090
Look at you... Geez.

14:18.090 --> 14:19.050
Is it from the troop?

14:19.460 --> 14:20.620
It's a troop indeed.

14:22.980 --> 14:24.790
But not ours.

14:25.020 --> 14:27.150
-Don't take it. -I will take it.

14:27.150 --> 14:29.230
I will answer it and ask her come here.

14:29.230 --> 14:30.000
When you meet her,

14:30.000 --> 14:31.510
you better settle it like a man!

14:31.510 --> 14:32.730
I'll buy you dinner. Steak!

14:33.560 --> 14:35.460
I make enough money to buy that myself.

14:35.460 --> 14:37.210
How about a drink? Wine aged for 17 years!

14:37.210 --> 14:38.600
17 years?

14:38.600 --> 14:39.880
That's an adolescent!

14:39.880 --> 14:41.830
I'll introduce my cousin to you! She flies.

14:41.830 --> 14:42.780
In the air force?

14:42.780 --> 14:43.650
A flight attendant.

14:43.650 --> 14:45.920
I have photos of her colleagues on my phone.

14:46.820 --> 14:47.720
You've been keeping that

14:47.720 --> 14:49.560
from me all this time?

14:50.440 --> 14:51.710
Your phone.

14:53.320 --> 14:54.460
Hurry up.

15:02.020 --> 15:03.900
Are you trying to fool me?

15:04.910 --> 15:08.230
You were searching the place without a pocket!

15:09.120 --> 15:10.240
Earlier...

15:16.180 --> 15:17.200
Are you all right?

15:20.550 --> 15:23.580
Excuse me. Is he the patient?

15:24.270 --> 15:26.770
Yes. I gave him first aid…

15:28.590 --> 15:30.180
Did you have your pocket picked?

15:30.180 --> 15:31.700
I'm going to kill him!

15:31.700 --> 15:32.910
You just said you felt sorry for him.

15:32.910 --> 15:34.510
What hospital was he?

15:42.530 --> 15:45.250
I said to take these off! It makes me look pathetic!

15:45.250 --> 15:48.100
Don't move. Let's take him inside as it is.

15:48.940 --> 15:50.080
Excuse me, sir.

15:50.080 --> 15:53.440
I told you I am fine. It doesn't hurt!

15:53.440 --> 15:56.810
Excuse me! He dropped this.

15:56.810 --> 15:59.300
Oh! Thank you.

16:04.560 --> 16:06.080
Hello?

16:06.080 --> 16:09.140
No. This is the Haesung Hospital Emergency Room.

16:09.140 --> 16:10.300
The owner of this phone

16:10.300 --> 16:12.350
met a motorcycle accident and was sent here just now.

16:12.850 --> 16:14.160
Are you his guardian?

16:21.050 --> 16:22.320
He was the patient of a motorcycle accident.

16:24.370 --> 16:25.620
His information is right here.

16:28.000 --> 16:29.360
Who wrote this?

16:29.770 --> 16:31.930
The guys who put me in this state.

16:32.440 --> 16:34.460
Please take these off me! Gosh.

16:34.460 --> 16:36.330
Ok. I got it. Don't move.

16:36.330 --> 16:37.660
Transfer him to our attention.

16:37.660 --> 16:38.350
Yes.

16:39.710 --> 16:41.950
Whoever gave you first aid did a great job.

16:42.140 --> 16:43.830
Very thorough and neat.

16:44.690 --> 16:48.290
Let me see. Possibly fractured ribs.

16:48.290 --> 16:50.130
That’s right. You have a fracture.

16:50.130 --> 16:55.070
The ankles... They are sprained.

16:56.400 --> 16:57.330
Are you a thief?

16:58.490 --> 17:00.200
As it puts here.

17:00.780 --> 17:04.109
He's a thief. Make him as painful as possible in the therapy.

17:04.430 --> 17:07.480
What are you talking about? I'm a victim here.

17:07.480 --> 17:09.980
Talk to your insurance company about your accident.

17:09.980 --> 17:12.230
We need to arrange a X-ray for you

17:12.230 --> 17:13.960
to check your ribs and ankles.

17:13.960 --> 17:15.740
The director wants to see you.

17:15.740 --> 17:17.740
OK. Call me when the result comes out.

17:17.740 --> 17:18.550
Okay.

17:23.589 --> 17:24.599
Here's your phone.

17:25.569 --> 17:27.349
You guardian called. I answered it for you.

17:27.349 --> 17:29.040
The X-ray requires some time.

17:29.040 --> 17:30.100
You can have a rest here.

17:45.930 --> 17:47.460
I have a really bad luck.

17:48.870 --> 17:50.700
I got shot while I was running away.

17:52.650 --> 17:54.940
It's not that. It's a long story.

17:56.680 --> 17:59.450
Anyway, come with your scooter.

18:02.350 --> 18:04.900
I’ve completed the research paper you resigned to me.

18:05.330 --> 18:09.390
Thank you for your hard work. Did you find it helpful?

18:10.120 --> 18:12.330
Yes. I learned a lot.

18:13.950 --> 18:16.120
Wow, your graphs look neat and organized.

18:17.210 --> 18:19.150
You have only your final interview left

18:19.150 --> 18:20.790
for your professor appointment, right?

18:20.790 --> 18:23.560
Yes, I'm preparing...

18:27.750 --> 18:29.450
for…

18:32.020 --> 18:34.760
I'm sorry. My patient is running away! So…

18:34.760 --> 18:36.770
Is he trying to run away

18:36.770 --> 18:37.890
without paying after receiving treatment?

18:37.890 --> 18:39.390
Yes, he's not received the treatment yet.

18:39.390 --> 18:40.400
If you are done...

18:40.400 --> 18:41.960
Okay, go get him.

18:41.960 --> 18:43.280
Heal him well.

18:43.280 --> 18:45.310
A good will comes before a good medical skill.

18:45.310 --> 18:47.150
Then, bye now.

18:50.490 --> 18:52.640
- Ms. Choi? - Yes?

18:52.990 --> 18:54.360
Where is the patient?

18:55.850 --> 18:57.420
Oh? He was here just now.

18:59.450 --> 19:01.960
Geez. I said I really have to go!

19:02.400 --> 19:03.180
If I'm here,

19:03.180 --> 19:05.120
the entire hospital will be in chaos!

19:05.530 --> 19:06.790
He ran away?

19:07.290 --> 19:08.350
And you didn't see that?

19:09.610 --> 19:10.530
I am sorry.

19:10.530 --> 19:12.080
He almost made it out of the parking lot.

19:12.080 --> 19:13.430
His ankles are even more swollen.

19:13.890 --> 19:16.040
This is so frustrating!

19:16.650 --> 19:18.320
If my boss catch me,

19:18.320 --> 19:19.670
I will be lying down in

19:19.670 --> 19:21.530
a mortuary, not an emergency room!

19:22.460 --> 19:23.370
What right does the hospital

19:23.370 --> 19:25.620
have to keep me here?

19:25.620 --> 19:27.880
Whether I stay or leave is up to me!

19:28.630 --> 19:31.080
It's not our right but our duty.

19:31.570 --> 19:32.590
If you want to leave,

19:32.590 --> 19:34.270
you need to sign an agreement to refuse treatment

19:34.270 --> 19:36.190
and pay off your bills.

19:36.190 --> 19:39.460
What? Why do I have to pay?

19:39.460 --> 19:40.740
I didn't do anything here.

19:41.070 --> 19:43.070
You received an examination here.

19:43.070 --> 19:44.230
You have to pay for that.

19:44.230 --> 19:45.980
- What if I don’t? - Then I'll call the police.

19:50.720 --> 19:52.520
You are so…

19:52.520 --> 19:53.950
Okay, fine.

19:53.950 --> 19:55.370
My friend is coming.

19:55.370 --> 19:56.130
I'll lie down here

19:56.130 --> 19:57.210
until he gets here.

19:57.960 --> 20:00.560
Sir, your bed is over there.

20:01.920 --> 20:03.640
Geez! I'm going to the bathroom!

20:03.640 --> 20:04.910
You expect me to believe that?

20:04.910 --> 20:06.860
I will be sure to pay, okay?

20:07.240 --> 20:08.720
I'll give you my phone.

20:09.560 --> 20:12.380
How troublesome you are. Let go off me.

20:13.570 --> 20:15.910
Gosh. They are so rude.

20:17.230 --> 20:19.450
The punk is so…

20:23.400 --> 20:26.830
Big Boss? Kidding me?

20:26.830 --> 20:28.710
All of them should be sent to

20:28.710 --> 20:30.250
the military so that they can grow up!

20:30.650 --> 20:32.440
- Let's get back to work! - Yes.

20:35.830 --> 20:37.770
He didn’t answer the call.

20:45.060 --> 20:46.670
If I catch you, you will be dead.

20:46.670 --> 20:50.780
So, are you going to confirm the location of the mortuary?

20:51.050 --> 20:53.300
What a thorough man.

20:55.830 --> 20:57.300
The emergency room is this way.

20:57.300 --> 20:58.830
I'm on my way.

21:05.230 --> 21:06.490
I'm out. Where are you?

21:09.500 --> 21:10.510
You’re here?

21:11.040 --> 21:12.880
-Please move. –Excuse me.

21:33.050 --> 21:34.150
It's going to sting.

21:34.810 --> 21:35.950
I'll stitch it up.

21:35.950 --> 21:37.730
Please get the tools ready.

21:37.730 --> 21:38.800
Sure.

21:41.500 --> 21:42.600
Excuse me.

21:44.670 --> 21:45.860
Hello?

21:50.370 --> 21:51.690
Hello?

22:00.610 --> 22:01.870
Are you Big Boss?

22:02.740 --> 22:03.830
Yes, I am.

22:04.530 --> 22:06.460
Why do you have that phone?

22:06.980 --> 22:08.680
A patient gave it to me.

22:09.780 --> 22:10.900
Are you his guardian?

22:10.900 --> 22:12.350
I'm not his guardian.

22:12.650 --> 22:13.980
I'm the owner of that phone.

22:13.980 --> 22:15.390
You can’t feel anything, right?

22:15.780 --> 22:16.930
I'm going to stitch it up now.

22:20.170 --> 22:21.540
Where is the patient of motorcycle accident?

22:22.900 --> 22:24.650
Oh? Where did he go?

22:25.580 --> 22:26.730
Maybe he's in the X-ray room?

22:32.250 --> 22:33.950
May I have your name?

22:34.900 --> 22:36.730
Are you the guys who want

22:36.730 --> 22:38.270
to send him to a mortuary?

22:38.270 --> 22:39.650
Did you say a mortuary?

22:42.140 --> 22:43.580
There must be a misunderstanding...

22:43.580 --> 22:46.800
Ms. Choi, tell these guys to wait outside.

22:47.440 --> 22:50.000
And tell the security guards to keep an eye on them.

22:53.930 --> 22:55.150
Hurry up!

22:55.150 --> 22:57.230
You can't be here. Please wait over there.

22:57.230 --> 22:58.400
Wait...

22:58.400 --> 22:59.720
Please.

23:24.060 --> 23:25.140
He gave the phone to her.

23:25.140 --> 23:26.740
Looks like he ran away.

23:28.300 --> 23:30.610
Yes. It seems so.

23:31.300 --> 23:32.390
Let’s find him outside.

23:33.370 --> 23:34.450
I don't think he went too far.

23:34.950 --> 23:37.740
No. Probably not.

23:38.750 --> 23:39.990
You can go now.

23:49.560 --> 23:53.740
Ouch! My stomach.

23:53.740 --> 23:56.420
My stomach suddenly… It seems to be appendicitis!

23:56.420 --> 23:58.670
- The appendix isn't on that side. – Oh. Here.

23:59.570 --> 24:00.680
What's wrong with me?

24:00.680 --> 24:02.240
Actually, the appendix is on that side.

24:09.420 --> 24:11.500
Gosh. You want to die?

24:12.460 --> 24:13.430
Let's go.

24:16.260 --> 24:18.100
They look like thugs, right?

24:18.100 --> 24:19.950
The big boss and his second hand.

24:21.720 --> 24:22.310
Maybe I pushed him

24:22.310 --> 24:23.660
too hard earlier.

24:24.340 --> 24:27.020
Don't worry. I'm better with a knife.

24:32.650 --> 24:34.140
Do you know where you are going?

24:34.140 --> 24:35.780
I think I do.

24:36.110 --> 24:37.940
I saw a gang earlier...

24:53.520 --> 24:55.400
Do you really have to find your phone?

24:55.890 --> 24:57.760
Those guys look good at fighting.

24:57.760 --> 24:59.520
I have a good reason to find it.

25:00.400 --> 25:01.430
Why?

25:02.800 --> 25:05.300
Do you have a secret on that phone?

25:06.640 --> 25:09.310
Something not honorable but nice?

25:09.310 --> 25:10.340
Yes.

25:12.010 --> 25:13.910
Hey, brothers!

25:14.880 --> 25:17.460
Everybody, drop it!

25:17.920 --> 25:19.780
Who are you?

25:19.780 --> 25:21.840
Just keep going your way.

25:21.840 --> 25:24.720
Don't interrupt a funeral.

25:26.950 --> 25:28.770
We have something to talk to him.

25:28.770 --> 25:30.010
Then get in line.

25:30.530 --> 25:32.710
Pathetic losers!

25:35.660 --> 25:37.520
Please save me.

25:38.450 --> 25:42.180
Hey, did you steal these guys' phones too?

25:44.380 --> 25:46.800
Why? Why they beat you

25:46.800 --> 25:48.450
Please save me!

25:49.070 --> 25:51.650
I'll return you your phone.

25:51.930 --> 25:55.240
Hey. See the number of these guys?

25:56.260 --> 25:58.330
Is this a fair trade to you?

25:58.940 --> 26:01.540
Ki Bum tried to leave the gang,

26:01.540 --> 26:03.560
so they wanted him to pay the membership fee.

26:04.160 --> 26:05.600
It’s five million won.

26:05.600 --> 26:06.890
For leaving the gang?

26:07.700 --> 26:11.150
Is it normal for that?

26:11.710 --> 26:13.270
Prices are going up.

26:14.590 --> 26:16.570
So you are in the same line of work as we are.

26:17.030 --> 26:17.670
You can search nothing

26:17.670 --> 26:19.300
from him.

26:19.300 --> 26:21.060
How about we two settle it?

26:21.060 --> 26:23.150
Good idea. Let’s settle it.

26:23.940 --> 26:24.550
Since it’s a money problem,

26:24.550 --> 26:25.740
let’s settle it with money.

26:27.800 --> 26:29.450
I have some here.

26:29.450 --> 26:31.500
Take this wallet from me if you dare.

26:31.500 --> 26:32.760
Then I'll give you all of it.

26:33.180 --> 26:34.870
- Really? - You mean it?

26:34.870 --> 26:36.300
You stay out of it.

26:37.020 --> 26:40.100
I mean it. I'm his brother.

26:42.240 --> 26:43.290
What's your name?

26:43.290 --> 26:45.480
Ki Bum. Kim Ki Bum.

26:46.960 --> 26:48.510
I'm Ki Bum's older brother.

26:49.220 --> 26:50.230
If you can take this wallet from me,

26:50.230 --> 26:51.380
I'll pay his fees.

26:51.960 --> 26:53.110
Take it.

26:57.470 --> 26:59.280
You're dead if that wallet is empty!

27:19.530 --> 27:22.520
Wow, you carry a knife with you?

27:26.440 --> 27:29.620
It can’t be. You guys sucks.

27:29.620 --> 27:31.000
Dissolve it.

27:33.300 --> 27:34.950
If you have a knife, take it out.

27:34.950 --> 27:36.630
If you have a gun, take it out too.

27:36.940 --> 27:38.520
Bring it on, all of you!

27:38.520 --> 27:40.130
We can beat them

27:40.130 --> 27:41.300
with all of us!

27:41.860 --> 27:42.990
Take out your knife!

27:49.450 --> 27:52.370
It was unnecessary to say that.

27:54.460 --> 27:55.850
I regret it now.

27:56.860 --> 27:58.500
At least none of them have a gun.

27:59.150 --> 28:00.370
Attack!

28:05.850 --> 28:06.910
Doctor, can you take a look at this?

28:07.590 --> 28:09.020
I think something is wrong with the lungs.

28:13.910 --> 28:15.800
The motorcycle accident patient...

28:16.350 --> 28:17.960
I think he ran away again.

28:20.310 --> 28:21.570
His guardian came.

28:21.570 --> 28:24.260
Again? Where is the guardian?

28:25.860 --> 28:27.380
Over there.

28:39.110 --> 28:40.500
Yoon Myung Joo?

28:43.750 --> 28:45.220
Kang Mo Yeon?

28:47.280 --> 28:49.410
Are you his guardian?

28:49.410 --> 28:50.820
Are you the doctor-in-charge?

28:51.600 --> 28:52.850
Where is he?

28:53.450 --> 28:54.840
Show me his history sheet first.

28:56.070 --> 28:56.880
Why came to other hospital

28:56.880 --> 28:58.730
to ask for other people’s history sheet.

28:59.660 --> 29:01.840
It seems that every time we meet each other,

29:01.840 --> 29:03.140
a man is involved.

29:03.140 --> 29:04.980
I have no time to joke around with you.

29:04.980 --> 29:06.410
Please give me his history sheet.

29:07.100 --> 29:08.350
He is important to me.

29:10.080 --> 29:11.320
Important?

29:11.320 --> 29:12.520
Is he severely hurt?

29:13.730 --> 29:14.380
As his doctor-in-charge,

29:14.380 --> 29:15.900
how could you not know your patient was missing?

29:16.600 --> 29:17.780
Where did he go?

29:19.130 --> 29:20.510
That's what I want to ask.

29:21.240 --> 29:23.060
It seems that he, who is very important to you,

29:23.060 --> 29:24.730
ran away without paying his bill.

29:25.280 --> 29:25.960
Since you are here,

29:25.960 --> 29:28.490
so why don't you pay for him ?

29:29.230 --> 29:32.550
Have the security guards to search the man's restrooms.

29:32.550 --> 29:33.520
Even you can’t find him,

29:33.520 --> 29:34.640
make sure

29:34.640 --> 29:36.010
she pays the bill.

29:36.010 --> 29:37.960
How can you just leave like that?

29:40.620 --> 29:42.500
Talk to Ms. Choi.

29:42.960 --> 29:44.130
We tried to have him stay

29:44.130 --> 29:45.820
for treatment twice.

29:45.820 --> 29:47.410
I believe we've done our part.

29:48.120 --> 29:49.250
I'm busy. Bye.

29:53.720 --> 29:54.730
Where's the men's restroom?

29:55.340 --> 29:56.610
Over there.

29:57.240 --> 30:00.830
This is huge! Yoon Myung Joo is in the Emergency Room.

30:00.830 --> 30:02.030
Yoon Myung Joo?

30:02.030 --> 30:03.380
You mean the one from the Military Academy?

30:03.380 --> 30:04.470
Yes, that bitch!

30:04.470 --> 30:05.670
We had our internships together

30:05.670 --> 30:07.730
when she was a visiting student!

30:07.730 --> 30:09.720
Yes, that beautiful girl, Yoon Myung Joo.

30:09.720 --> 30:11.550
The one who stole the man you admired.

30:12.460 --> 30:15.600
Hey, who is beautiful?

30:15.600 --> 30:18.060
Just because of her big eyes and big nose?

30:18.060 --> 30:19.990
Just because she has a pretty face?

30:20.340 --> 30:21.760
It's her makeup.

30:21.760 --> 30:23.690
- She is beautiful without it. - What?

30:25.240 --> 30:25.990
Actually he didn't go out

30:25.990 --> 30:28.080
with Yoon Myung Joo.

30:28.080 --> 30:30.320
Let it be the past.

30:30.320 --> 30:31.570
Anyway, why is she here? Is she hurt?

30:32.180 --> 30:34.930
No, her boyfriend got hurt.

30:34.930 --> 30:37.070
And her boyfriend is probably

30:37.070 --> 30:38.670
about 20 years old at the most.

30:38.670 --> 30:39.850
She must be crazy.

30:39.850 --> 30:42.610
What are you talking about? Her boyfriend is a soldier.

30:43.050 --> 30:45.110
No way. He's got long hair.

30:45.110 --> 30:48.170
He is a soldier. He’s famous in the army.

30:48.170 --> 30:49.950
Everyone knows about their love story.

30:49.950 --> 30:51.450
Her boyfriend is a lieutenant.

30:51.450 --> 30:54.920
Lieutenant? What's that?

30:54.920 --> 30:58.030
You know there are ranks in the military, like lieutenant, captain, and such.

30:58.030 --> 30:59.040
You idiot.

30:59.040 --> 31:01.820
You are the weird one who knows that kind of stuff. Not me.

31:01.820 --> 31:02.510
Anyway,

31:02.510 --> 31:03.900
her boyfriend's a master sergeant

31:03.900 --> 31:05.840
and doesn't have a college degree.

31:05.840 --> 31:07.840
But Myung Joo is an officer

31:07.840 --> 31:09.010
and an army doctor!

31:09.010 --> 31:10.700
Her father is a general with three stars.

31:10.700 --> 31:12.510
Do you think they would get along?

31:13.270 --> 31:14.460
Really?

31:16.510 --> 31:20.220
Then who is that guy who gave me his cell phone and ran away?

31:27.690 --> 31:28.930
What happened to him?

31:29.500 --> 31:31.800
Ms. Choi, call Dr. Kang! Hurry.

31:33.460 --> 31:34.810
There was an incident.

31:44.820 --> 31:45.800
What happened?

31:47.800 --> 31:49.320
I heard you were hurt, but you look just fine.

31:51.700 --> 31:52.840
Follow me.

32:02.780 --> 32:03.890
What happened to him?

32:03.890 --> 32:04.720
What's wrong?

32:04.720 --> 32:06.050
We had an incident.

32:06.490 --> 32:08.220
An unfortunate incident near the hospital.

32:08.710 --> 32:10.570
You don't call this an incident. He got beat up.

32:11.290 --> 32:13.560
Did the two of you adults do this to a kid?

32:13.920 --> 32:15.170
Nonsense…

32:15.490 --> 32:17.540
Who did this to you?

32:17.540 --> 32:19.190
Did he do it?

32:19.190 --> 32:22.500
No, he didn't. He saved me.

32:23.150 --> 32:26.480
Sir, you are in a hospital. It's okay.

32:27.110 --> 32:29.640
We have a security team. You can tell me the truth.

32:29.640 --> 32:31.160
Did this man beat you?

32:31.560 --> 32:34.740
I told you he didn't do it.

32:39.370 --> 32:42.740
Even though he says no, you won't believe it, right?

32:48.450 --> 32:49.690
I'll give you a painkiller.

32:50.000 --> 32:52.330
And I'll arrange you a A-ray of your whole body.

32:52.780 --> 32:54.220
Ms. Ha, when you're done dressing him...

32:54.220 --> 32:56.930
Don't worry. I'll take him myself.

32:57.320 --> 32:58.710
Ms. Choi, call the security.

32:58.710 --> 33:00.620
I'll check the CCTV footage.

33:00.620 --> 33:02.120
I will call the police.

33:05.000 --> 33:07.270
Oh? Excuse me! Wait!

33:08.150 --> 33:10.170
Excuse me! Wait!

33:13.680 --> 33:14.750
Step aside.

33:14.920 --> 33:17.270
I will after I clear up the misunderstanding.

33:19.200 --> 33:21.290
That kid told you the truth.

33:21.290 --> 33:22.120
That kid...

33:22.120 --> 33:23.890
Is my patient your kid?

33:31.830 --> 33:35.550
Your patient stole my colleague's phone.

33:35.550 --> 33:37.760
So we came here to get the phone back.

33:38.390 --> 33:39.660
And we saw he was being beaten up by a gang,

33:39.660 --> 33:40.810
so we saved him.

33:40.810 --> 33:43.580
You saved the man who stole your phone?

33:44.570 --> 33:47.720
It would make more sense for you to beat him up.

33:50.460 --> 33:51.580
Is this 112?

33:51.580 --> 33:52.980
This is the Haesung Hospital Emergency...

34:13.179 --> 34:14.370
What are you doing?

34:14.370 --> 34:16.500
Let me be straightforward.

34:17.150 --> 34:18.940
You can't call the police.

34:19.710 --> 34:20.600
Right?

34:21.989 --> 34:22.920
Give me my phone.

34:25.449 --> 34:27.630
Actually, we are soldiers.

34:28.159 --> 34:30.170
We are on vacation.

34:30.170 --> 34:33.040
It'll be a bother if we get involved in an assault.

34:33.040 --> 34:34.790
There'll be a lot of paperwork to do.

34:35.870 --> 34:37.420
Please help us.

34:37.960 --> 34:40.050
Why should I?

34:40.050 --> 34:42.440
I don't care if you are a soldier or a thug.

34:42.940 --> 34:44.420
I said to hand me my phone.

34:49.370 --> 34:51.429
You won't believe this

34:51.429 --> 34:52.530
since all Korean men have this one.

34:54.889 --> 34:58.390
If you say this is an counterfeit,

34:58.390 --> 34:59.440
then I can't argue back.

35:00.870 --> 35:02.010
Where did you go to school?

35:03.130 --> 35:04.480
Since this is Haesung Hospital,

35:04.480 --> 35:05.990
did you graduate from Myung In University?

35:06.370 --> 35:07.380
Why do you ask me that?

35:07.380 --> 35:09.490
Do you know Yoon Myung Joo?

35:09.490 --> 35:10.930
You may graduate in the same year.

35:13.790 --> 35:15.210
How do you know her?

35:17.780 --> 35:22.080
Are you the... Master Sergeant, Sergeant,

35:22.080 --> 35:24.550
Corporal.. something like that.

35:24.550 --> 35:27.960
-And Security Officer? -Right. Security Officer.

35:28.860 --> 35:30.080
Are you that man?

35:32.980 --> 35:35.760
I'm not that man, but come with me.

35:37.320 --> 35:39.160
Myung Joo will confirm my identity.

35:45.540 --> 35:47.020
It's been a long time.

35:48.060 --> 35:49.360
Yes, it has been.

35:50.870 --> 35:53.590
It must be so hard for you to hide from me.

35:53.950 --> 35:55.240
But you look well.

35:55.910 --> 35:56.770
Yes.

35:58.020 --> 35:58.850
When can we talk without

35:58.850 --> 36:00.380
thinking about our military ranks?

36:02.910 --> 36:04.240
Oh, maybe you would totally ignore me

36:04.240 --> 36:05.350
if I didn't have my rank.

36:05.350 --> 36:06.290
Yes, ma'am.

36:06.290 --> 36:08.130
I want to kill you!

36:08.550 --> 36:10.300
How much longer will you avoid me?

36:10.790 --> 36:12.620
Why didn't you answer my calls?

36:14.060 --> 36:14.800
Why won't you even let me know

36:14.800 --> 36:16.470
if you are alive or dead?

36:18.050 --> 36:19.970
When can you stop running away from me?

36:22.560 --> 36:26.160
Answer me. I'm not asking you because I don't know the answer.

36:28.080 --> 36:33.290
Just... Let me hear your voice at least.

36:34.920 --> 36:37.430
My answer isn't what you think it is.

36:39.420 --> 36:40.430
Please don't assume that

36:40.430 --> 36:43.100
I left because of you.

36:44.710 --> 36:46.320
My feeling changed.

36:48.390 --> 36:50.970
No reason but that.

36:53.060 --> 36:54.520
That's all.

36:55.420 --> 36:56.390
I don't believe it.

36:56.650 --> 36:57.790
If you are done...

36:57.790 --> 37:00.680
- Don't do that. -I got to go.

37:02.300 --> 37:05.090
Don't you dare. Stop right there!

37:05.380 --> 37:06.830
Stop right there, Seo Dae Young!

37:07.950 --> 37:09.390
Master Sergeant Seo Dae Young.

37:10.440 --> 37:12.450
You didn't even salute to your senior!

37:40.090 --> 37:41.310
Stand right there.

37:42.710 --> 37:44.080
Stand like that all night.

37:45.110 --> 37:46.870
Stand like that until you die.

37:49.140 --> 37:51.450
I will never take your salute.

38:03.910 --> 38:07.280
You… You’re abusing your power.

38:07.630 --> 38:09.550
I'm trying to train a solider of weak mental power.

38:11.080 --> 38:12.180
What brought you here?

38:13.490 --> 38:16.200
I am here to restore my reputation.

38:17.520 --> 38:20.490
I need you to verify my identity.

38:20.490 --> 38:21.920
She won't believe me.

38:23.140 --> 38:24.030
It's easier to trust

38:24.030 --> 38:26.110
an acquaintance than a stranger. Tell me.

38:27.190 --> 38:28.370
Is that so?

38:29.950 --> 38:33.280
Then report these two men to the police.

38:34.180 --> 38:35.230
They are deserters.

38:38.590 --> 38:39.550
Hey, you!

38:42.180 --> 38:43.690
Please return my cell phone.

38:43.690 --> 38:45.050
Your identity has been verified.

38:46.050 --> 38:47.050
Give it back to him.

38:49.870 --> 38:50.930
Since it happened this way

38:51.630 --> 38:53.850
I am going to find out what's on this phone.

38:57.660 --> 38:58.910
Is everything clear now?

38:58.910 --> 39:01.620
Now I know who you are. But the assault is another thing.

39:01.860 --> 39:02.950
Follow me.

39:08.420 --> 39:10.430
It'll take about five minutes to find the footage.

39:10.750 --> 39:11.880
Please wait here.

39:11.880 --> 39:12.610
Sure.

39:40.740 --> 39:43.440
Exactly how do you know Myung Joo?

39:45.680 --> 39:46.320
We went to the same Military Academy.

39:46.320 --> 39:47.620
I was the senior.

39:49.410 --> 39:50.820
Do you have to know that even after

39:50.820 --> 39:52.270
you had my identity verified?

39:53.450 --> 39:55.030
I am not good at lying.

39:56.330 --> 39:58.240
Killers usually look charming.

40:02.670 --> 40:04.870
That's true.

40:06.380 --> 40:07.400
You’re so serious suddenly,

40:07.400 --> 40:08.340
which makes me scared.

40:08.340 --> 40:09.720
And there are only two of us here.

40:10.390 --> 40:11.830
Don't worry.

40:12.180 --> 40:15.840
My principle is that I must protect beautiful women, seniors, and children.

40:15.840 --> 40:18.830
I am relieved that I am one of them.

40:19.540 --> 40:20.340
You are not.

40:20.760 --> 40:22.570
A senior, I said!

40:30.220 --> 40:33.810
Big Boss, what is your name?

40:34.700 --> 40:37.320
I'm Yoo Shi Jin.

40:39.000 --> 40:40.410
What about you?

40:43.630 --> 40:44.620
I'm Kang Mo Yeon.

40:46.190 --> 40:47.290
Nice to meet you.

41:11.680 --> 41:13.690
Don't pretend to be nice.

41:17.550 --> 41:18.650
You just looked me in the eye.

41:20.700 --> 41:24.180
What kind of sport did you learn?

41:25.900 --> 41:27.940
I did judo until I was in eleventh grade.

41:29.470 --> 41:31.310
Why didn't you pay back?

41:34.520 --> 41:38.200
In that way it would end sooner.

41:39.110 --> 41:40.930
By the way, how did you know I did a sport?

41:40.930 --> 41:42.930
I saw how you were beaten up.

41:45.060 --> 41:46.680
You learn how to be beaten before learning how to beat someone.

41:48.570 --> 41:50.140
I did taekwondo.

41:50.140 --> 41:51.150
All the way to high school.

41:52.410 --> 41:58.000
Were you good?

41:58.000 --> 42:00.610
Well, I once won a gold medal.

42:00.610 --> 42:01.860
Mr. Kim Ki Bum, is your guardian here?

42:01.860 --> 42:03.550
We need to admit you.

42:04.300 --> 42:05.470
I said I have no guardian.

42:11.840 --> 42:13.980
I’m his guardian.

42:15.770 --> 42:16.870
Oh my god!

42:30.040 --> 42:31.090
Oh my god!

42:34.450 --> 42:35.900
Geez!

42:38.090 --> 42:39.620
Good! Just like that!

42:39.620 --> 42:40.560
Good job!

42:53.030 --> 42:54.470
That's right! Good!

42:57.430 --> 42:59.010
Great! Just like that!

42:59.560 --> 43:00.690
Now I know what happened.

43:02.440 --> 43:03.820
I'm sorry for misunderstanding you.

43:03.820 --> 43:05.100
You are? Then can you treat me?

43:05.100 --> 43:06.260
I feel pain.

43:07.290 --> 43:08.760
Where does it hurt?

43:10.180 --> 43:11.350
Right here.

43:13.180 --> 43:14.410
-Right here? –Ouch.

43:16.680 --> 43:18.440
Too much.

43:19.640 --> 43:20.780
I am serious.

43:34.950 --> 43:36.050
Looks like your stitches broke

43:36.050 --> 43:37.640
when you were fighting earlier.

43:38.430 --> 43:39.600
When did you get hurt?

43:42.450 --> 43:43.320
A few days ago.

43:44.180 --> 43:45.390
How did you get hurt?

43:47.150 --> 43:48.370
I was shoveling in the camp.

43:49.710 --> 43:51.200
Soldiers shovel a lot.

43:51.970 --> 43:55.610
Is that so? That's a strange troop.

43:55.610 --> 43:57.570
You got shot while shoveling?

43:58.170 --> 43:59.690
This is a wound from a gunshot.

44:01.340 --> 44:03.960
Have you seen gunshot wounds?

44:03.960 --> 44:05.770
Not in Korea.

44:05.770 --> 44:08.410
I saw them when I was volunteering in Africa.

44:13.250 --> 44:15.200
I'm telling you this since you know.

44:15.880 --> 44:19.040
I got this wound from Normandy.

44:21.570 --> 44:24.740
Bullets were pouring down like rain.

44:24.740 --> 44:28.620
I threw myself into them to save my comrade.

44:29.320 --> 44:33.110
Was your comrade Private Ryan?

44:41.460 --> 44:42.530
It's all stitched up.

44:43.000 --> 44:45.160
The stitches will be removed in a week.

44:45.160 --> 44:48.100
Until then, it needs disinfecting every day.

44:48.100 --> 44:49.520
There's a hospital in the military, right?

44:49.520 --> 44:50.980
Can I just come here?

44:52.350 --> 44:54.080
- Isn't it far? - It's far.

44:55.360 --> 44:56.790
Can I come every day?

44:56.790 --> 44:59.310
Every day is a bit much.

44:59.310 --> 45:01.720
Maybe three or four times a week? Then it'll heal up fast.

45:03.440 --> 45:04.690
Are you my doctor-in-charge?

45:04.690 --> 45:05.790
It's just disinfection.

45:05.790 --> 45:07.230
Does it matter who’s the doctor-in-charge?

45:08.700 --> 45:09.810
It matters.

45:11.380 --> 45:14.060
Especially the doctor's looks do.

45:17.110 --> 45:18.110
If you choose your doctor

45:18.110 --> 45:19.130
based on her looks,

45:19.290 --> 45:20.600
you can't get anyone better.

45:21.580 --> 45:22.700
I'll make an appointment for you.

45:22.700 --> 45:23.760
Come at 2:00 p.m.

45:29.490 --> 45:30.000
Being a doctor,

45:30.000 --> 45:32.690
you must not have a boyfriend, since you are too busy.

45:35.610 --> 45:36.170
Being a soldier,

45:36.170 --> 45:39.000
you must not have a girlfriend, since your work is hard.

45:41.580 --> 45:43.150
Who's going to answer here?

46:09.210 --> 46:12.550
Vice-Captain, which one is better?

46:12.860 --> 46:15.140
- Show me the one on the right. - This?

46:15.600 --> 46:17.440
Where are you going all dressed up?

46:18.240 --> 46:21.270
I'm going to Haesung Hospital the day after tomorrow.

46:21.270 --> 46:22.440
There are medics here,

46:22.440 --> 46:23.440
but he wants to travel

46:23.440 --> 46:25.040
over an hour for disinfection.

46:26.350 --> 46:28.150
Body strength concerns to country strength.

46:28.150 --> 46:29.550
I need to be treated

46:29.550 --> 46:30.770
by Korea's best doctors and equipment

46:30.770 --> 46:32.750
at Haesung Hospital,

46:32.750 --> 46:35.700
so that I can have a strong will to safeguard the country.

46:37.130 --> 46:38.490
The doctor must be pretty.

46:40.240 --> 46:42.030
There aren't any pretty doctors here.

46:42.030 --> 46:42.760
There is one.

46:44.000 --> 46:44.860
I know who that is.

46:44.860 --> 46:46.330
It's First Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo.

46:46.690 --> 46:49.510
Gosh, she's really beautiful!

46:49.850 --> 46:50.670
I heard her

46:50.670 --> 46:52.100
boyfriend dumped her!

46:52.500 --> 46:53.770
I want to see his face.

46:53.770 --> 46:56.090
Who that jerk is!

46:58.670 --> 47:00.050
What's wrong?

47:00.050 --> 47:04.520
Curiosity killed the cat!

47:06.290 --> 47:08.790
Am I a cat?

47:10.180 --> 47:12.140
I'm going to the hospital too.

47:13.020 --> 47:14.110
Give me a ride.

47:14.900 --> 47:16.360
For what?

47:19.810 --> 47:21.400
It's been fully paid.

47:23.010 --> 47:24.580
Soldiers don't make much money.

47:27.650 --> 47:28.780
Take care of your body.

47:28.920 --> 47:31.700
If you do bad things, I will catch you.

47:34.820 --> 47:35.900
I'm going in for the treatment.

47:40.940 --> 47:42.020
Don't forget your medicine.

47:42.850 --> 47:44.560
Make sure you eat before you take it.

47:45.510 --> 47:47.620
Thank you for paying.

47:48.720 --> 47:49.840
But I can't repay you.

47:50.920 --> 47:51.920
And don't try to lecture me

47:51.920 --> 47:53.590
just because you paid...

47:53.590 --> 47:57.470
I won't. Go. Bye.

47:58.830 --> 48:00.520
Wait.

48:03.880 --> 48:09.070
Sorry. I stole your phone.

48:09.070 --> 48:10.820
Okay. I got it.

48:12.500 --> 48:15.530
Wait.

48:17.690 --> 48:20.880
Getting beaten doesn't work. Paying them money doesn't either.

48:22.800 --> 48:26.600
How did you... get out of it?

48:31.520 --> 48:33.680
I ran away to a place where they could never find me.

48:34.520 --> 48:36.470
Where is that?

48:45.860 --> 48:47.120
Please move out of the way!

48:47.850 --> 48:50.100
Ms. Ha, we need more blood!

48:50.100 --> 48:51.840
I will get five more bags for now.

48:53.560 --> 48:55.180
Move out of the way!

48:57.300 --> 48:58.660
Please speed up!

50:33.440 --> 50:34.320
Hello?

50:34.730 --> 50:38.750
Mr. Yoo Shi Jin? This is Kang Mo Yeon.

50:39.870 --> 50:41.380
Are you done with the surgery?

50:41.380 --> 50:44.760
Yes. I heard you came today.

50:45.150 --> 50:47.040
This is the first time I was ever stood up by a doctor.

50:49.510 --> 50:51.500
It was emergency surgery.

50:52.510 --> 50:54.720
- Did he live? - Pardon?

50:54.720 --> 50:56.480
That patient who needed the surgery.

50:58.100 --> 51:00.180
Yes, I saved him.

51:01.290 --> 51:02.400
That's cool.

51:03.970 --> 51:05.630
Is this your personal number?

51:07.270 --> 51:08.190
Yes.

51:09.410 --> 51:10.660
You figured out my number.

51:11.240 --> 51:12.950
Save my number.

51:15.330 --> 51:16.720
I don't want to miss you tomorrow.

51:18.910 --> 51:20.880
Are you always so straightforward like this?

51:21.490 --> 51:23.480
I meant for my treatment.

51:24.080 --> 51:27.100
Yeah, that's what I meant too.

51:27.100 --> 51:28.250
No, you didn't.

51:29.290 --> 51:31.050
You don't trust your doctor?

51:32.440 --> 51:33.890
Did you take your medicine?

51:34.110 --> 51:37.510
Will it hurt more if I don't take it?

51:38.170 --> 51:39.640
Will I need to be hospitalized or something?

51:41.540 --> 51:42.950
What time do you want to come tomorrow?

51:46.290 --> 51:49.840
Instead... Do you want to see me now?

51:57.290 --> 51:58.300
You don't want to?

52:00.520 --> 52:02.880
Yes, I do. Come now.

53:09.410 --> 53:11.790
Hello, sir. My current location is

53:11.790 --> 53:13.140
Haesung Hospital in Gangnam.

53:13.810 --> 53:15.230
Yes, I will be on standby.

53:16.080 --> 53:17.220
Yes, sir.

53:22.780 --> 53:23.890
Are you here?

53:23.890 --> 53:25.830
Yes, I am here.

53:25.830 --> 53:27.740
But I have to leave for an urgent matter.

53:28.760 --> 53:31.880
You're leaving? Where are you now?

53:31.880 --> 53:33.060
I'm on the rooftop.

53:33.420 --> 53:36.800
On the rooftop? What rooftop?

53:42.390 --> 53:43.430
What are you doing here?

53:46.070 --> 53:49.490
I am sorry. But I have to stand you up this time.

53:55.070 --> 53:57.480
It must be an emergency. Let's go downstairs...

53:57.480 --> 54:00.980
No. They are here to pick me up.

54:01.040 --> 54:03.560
They are here for you? For what?

54:04.970 --> 54:06.500
Did a war break out?

54:10.570 --> 54:11.770
It did happen somewhere.

54:12.460 --> 54:14.410
But it's not here. Don't worry.

54:14.770 --> 54:17.040
What is it then? Why is a helicopter taking you?

54:17.040 --> 54:18.560
I'll explain it next time.

54:19.540 --> 54:20.940
But promise me one thing.

54:34.290 --> 54:36.580
I want to see you next weekend.

54:37.080 --> 54:38.400
Not at the hospital, but somewhere else.

54:38.880 --> 54:40.390
Aren't you coming for your treatment?

54:40.390 --> 54:42.090
I'll be back healthy!

54:43.490 --> 54:45.360
Let's go to see a movie!

54:51.550 --> 54:53.430
Answer me. I don't have much time!

54:55.260 --> 54:56.350
Would you like to or not?

54:58.670 --> 54:59.870
I would like to go.

55:01.060 --> 55:02.340
You promised.

56:44.150 --> 56:45.990
We are in the battle zone.

56:45.990 --> 56:48.140
Now we're on a combat-mode flight.

56:54.840 --> 56:56.010
How long have we been on the plane?

56:56.550 --> 56:58.080
It's been seven hours.

57:00.000 --> 57:02.080
-Then the final destination must be... -Yes.

57:14.540 --> 57:16.960
-Harry Potter. -Corporal Gong Chul Ho.

57:16.960 --> 57:19.310
The mosquitoes in this area are vicious. Be careful.

57:19.310 --> 57:20.700
Yes, sir.

57:23.920 --> 57:25.900
By the way, why are we taking off…?

57:26.460 --> 57:27.500
It’s our identification tag.

57:27.500 --> 57:29.000
If we are killed during the operation,

57:29.000 --> 57:30.380
we must not carry any identification.

58:06.120 --> 58:07.660
Where are we?

58:11.530 --> 58:12.890
Afghanistan.

59:03.960 --> 59:07.390
-=Next Episode=-

59:07.390 --> 59:09.020
This isn't a practice. It's a real battle.

59:09.020 --> 59:10.790
We may kill and we may be killed.

59:10.790 --> 59:12.030
Did you miss me?

59:12.560 --> 59:15.040
Of course I did. What about you?

59:15.040 --> 59:16.370
I miss you a lot.

59:16.370 --> 59:18.780
I wasn't going to call you.

59:18.780 --> 59:21.060
Aren't you ashamed of yourself?

59:21.840 --> 59:23.930
We decided to dispatch Alpha Team.

59:23.930 --> 59:25.640
To where, sir?

59:25.640 --> 59:28.290
I'm thinking of putting Dr. Kang in

59:28.290 --> 59:29.960
charge of the volunteer medical team.

59:29.960 --> 59:31.100
A suspicious explosive

59:31.100 --> 59:31.870
was found in virgin area.

59:31.870 --> 59:35.270
So you're doing the kind of work that could kill you,

59:35.270 --> 59:36.810
Yoo Shi Jin.
